title: Himi 66
lyrics:
M.NG.
1.
Ko e ‘Eiki anga lelei
‘Oku kei tatali,
Ke ne fakamolemole
‘A e angakovi.
2.
Pea te u talia leva
‘Ene anga ‘ofa.
Kuo fakahā totonu
‘I he Folofola.
3.
Pea u li’aki fehi’a
‘Eku paongata’a.
Pea u fakatonutonu
‘Eku fuakava.
4.
Pea u tuku hoku loto
Ki hoku ‘Otua,
‘I he mālohi ‘o Sīsū,
Ko hoku hūfanga. *
